10/03/2008
ANKARA, Turkey -- Police say sniffer dogs helped discover 255kg of heroin hidden in a truck during a routine check at the Iranian border Sunday (March 9th). 
The driver of the truck, an Iranian national, was arrested. 
Turkey is one of the main routes for moving drugs from the Middle East and Central Asia to Europe. 
(AP, Turkish Daily News - 09/03/08)
